column5: This is why I don’t trust humans

I feel exactly the same but I thought that I struggled to remember things because of my adhd. But it doesn’t feel right cuz I forget everything and my grammar has also got worse and my speech and people don’t understand what I’m saying too. I have tested my iq and it’s also over average. My teachers have said to me that I’m intelligent because I never study and I made it through high school and my mom also tell me that. But I feel lost and stupid and I don’t feel like myself.
Upvote if it is ur dream gurl
